2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the performance of different adaptive transmission techniques in a cooperative communication system, which is a relevant topic in networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper analyzes the capacity of a communication system with decode-and-forward relaying, which involves control and optimization of the transmission parameters. 
4. cs.COMM (Communication and Networking) - The paper deals with the capacity analysis of a cooperative communication system, which is a core topic in communication and networking. 
5. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper discusses the performance of different adaptive transmission techniques in a cooperative communication system, which can be viewed as a multiagent system where the agents are the source, relay, and destination nodes.
